12:T480,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"VideoObject","name":"Whoza.ai for Joiners & Carpenters — AI Call Answering Demo","description":"Watch Katie capture a missed joinery enquiry in under 60 seconds. Bespoke kitchen project details collected, sent to WhatsApp, and ready for quoting while the carpenter is still on site.","thumbnailUrl":["https://whoza.ai/og-image.png","https://whoza.ai/og-image-1200x630.png"],"uploadDate":"2026-05-06T00:00:00+00:00","duration":"PT60S","contentUrl":"https://whoza.ai/whoza-explainer.mp4","embedUrl":"https://whoza.ai/for-joiners","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Whoza.ai","url":"https://whoza.ai","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://whoza.ai/logo.png","width":512,"height":512}},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Whoza.ai","url":"https://whoza.ai"},"potentialAction":{"@type":"WatchAction","target":{"@type":"EntryPoint","urlTemplate":"https://whoza.ai/for-joiners","actionPlatform":["http://schema.org/DesktopWebPlatform","http://schema.org/MobileWebPlatform"]},"expectsAcceptanceOf":{"@type":"Offer","price":"0","priceCurrency":"GBP","availability":"https://schema.org/InStock"}}}15:T1039,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How much does AI call answering cost for joiners?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"whoza.ai starts at <a href=\"/pricing\" className=\"text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline\">plans start at £59/month</a> for the Starter plan. That's less than one bespoke kitchen consultation. You get unlimited AI call answering, WhatsApp delivery, and a 7-day free trial with no credit card required. Most joiners recover the cost within a week by capturing just one missed project enquiry."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does AI call answering work?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Katie uses advanced AI to answer your business calls 24/7, capture customer details, and send structured alerts to your WhatsApp. Read our <a href=\"/blog/ai-call-answering-uk-tradespeople-definitive-guide-2026\" className=\"text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline\">complete guide to AI call answering</a> for UK trades to learn more."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can Katie handle bespoke furniture enquiries?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Absolutely. Katie is trained to handle detailed joinery enquiries including bespoke kitchens, fitted wardrobes, staircases, doors, and cabinets. She captures project type, materials preference, budget range, timeline, and dimensions — giving you a full brief before you even call back. Customers describing complex projects are guided through the key details Katie needs to collect."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What information does Katie collect from joinery customers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Katie captures: full name, phone number, postcode, project type (kitchen, wardrobe, staircase, door, window, etc.), materials preference (hardwood, oak, walnut, pine, MDF), budget range, timeline, property type (house/flat/commercial), and whether it's a commercial or residential client. For bespoke projects, she also asks about style preferences and whether plans or drawings are available."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Will customers know they're talking to AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Katie introduces herself as your digital assistant with a natural, professional voice. Most callers appreciate the instant response over voicemail or a ringing phone. In user surveys, 89% of callers are satisfied with the AI experience — they just want their joinery project discussed promptly and professionally."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does it work with my existing business phone number?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. You simply set up call forwarding from your existing joinery business number to your whoza.ai number. Your customers dial the same number they've always used — Katie just answers when you can't. Setup takes under 10 minutes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How quickly can I get set up?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Most joiners are live and capturing calls within 30 minutes. Sign up, connect your number via call forwarding, set your greeting and business details, and Katie starts answering immediately. No hardware, no IT team, no technical knowledge required."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can Katie handle commercial joinery contracts?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Katie identifies commercial enquiries from builders, developers, architects, and interior designers. She captures project scale, contract value, timeline, and decision-maker details. Commercial enquiries are tagged as priority in your WhatsApp alert so you can follow up fast — these are often your highest-value jobs."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What happens if Katie can't handle a complex enquiry?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Katie is trained to recognise when a call needs human attention. For complex bespoke projects or unusual situations, she takes a detailed message and flags it for your immediate callback. You receive the full context in WhatsApp so you can call back prepared with all the details — no more 'can you tell me about your project again' conversations."}}]}7:["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$12"}}],["$","$L13",null,{}],["$","$L14",null,{"items":[{"name":"Home","item":"https://whoza.ai"},{"name":"For Joiners & Carpenters","item":"https://whoza.ai/for-joiners"}]}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$15"}}],"$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b"],null,"$L1c"]}]
